title: God Has Made You More Than A Conqueror | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: God Has Made You More Than A Conqueror | Victoria Osteen
description:
We don't have to stay captive to our thoughts. When you choose to think the thoughts of Heaven, you'll live like the champion God created you to be!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
